{"tid":46132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊fb live寫tag自讚「破案神速」","createTime":"2016-12-19T12:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T15:02:44.000Z","uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82dc4bc9b2d912a90a1ec166ed176ce1c0a656aa","tid":46132,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161219&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56067875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161219%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56067875&d=dM30yAcC%2B%2F4wfHYmLqsYTHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=18b95949\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161219%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56067875&h=3d6ea57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161219&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56067875</a><br />\n九龍城城南道近太子道西昨晚的嚴重傷人案，警方今日凌晨在葵涌及黃大仙拘捕2名分別姓徐（35歲）及姓余（21歲）的男子，遇襲的35歲何姓男傷者經13小時搶救後不治，警方遂將案件改列謀殺，交由九龍城警區重案組調查，下午又在facebook專頁直播見記者簡報案情，並在帖文的hashtag自讚「#破案神速」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/203429_950edd1901e3fbe2bd2d05f281b5766c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F203429_950edd1901e3fbe2bd2d05f281b5766c.jpg&h=5a62cdf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成班人識既又有cam影晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338bc4963b4c092bed258eeb5706a7d6988665f1","tid":46132,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:37:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4996cf60a9860da89548da6efb7333f4e2c7eb2","tid":46132,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2e3026174b2043dbff41ea0bff15224753c349","tid":46132,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:02: